  <brief_title>Observational Study in Patients Who Underwent an Haploidentical Transplantation With T-repleted Bone Marrow</brief_title>
  <official_title>Retrospective-prospective Observational Study for Data Collection of Patients Who Underwent an Haploidentical Transplantation After Non-myeloablative Conditioning Regimen</official_title>
